参考:
Linux 下一步步安装 Git Server
http://aoingl.iteye.com/blog/1365201

安装：
$ apt-get install git-core

服务端创建git仓库：
~/git/repositories$ git init --bare develop-docs

初始化git仓库：
~/Documents/com/develop$ mkdir docs
~/Documents/com/develop$ cd docs/
~/Documents/com/develop/docs$ git init
~/Documents/com/develop/docs$ git remote add origin ~/git/repositories/develop-docs/

提交文件：
~/Documents/com/develop/docs$ touch Readme
~/Documents/com/develop/docs$ git add Readme
~/Documents/com/develop/docs$ git commit -m "add Readme"
~/Documents/com/develop/docs$ git push origin master
~/Documents/com/develop/docs$ git pull origin master

~/Documents/com/develop/docs$ vim .git/config  # 指定分支
---------------------------------------------
[branch "master"]
	remote = origin
	merge = refs/heads/master
---------------------------------------------
~/Documents/com/develop/docs$ git push
~/Documents/com/develop/docs$ git pull

克隆到本地：
~/Documents/com/develop$ git clone ~/git/repositories/develop-docs
~/Documents/com/develop$ git clone ~/git/repositories/develop-docs docs

